{"tid":2023723,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"2020年既你，認為64到底關唔關自己事？","createTime":"2020-05-19T07:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T17:56:06.000Z","uid":63822,"like":21,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"69a23387e04b16e5ae4fcbfcbef59d9c334ec9ad","tid":2023723,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聲援被打壓同胞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊撚個同你同胞，關我撚事"},{"pid":"1b3101c9cc60f48330b9b9488b88db7b430a6626","tid":2023723,"uid":315626,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:31:25.000Z","msg":"攻擊支那既子彈"},{"pid":"05fb8abe9f79b2e127000e58958dc967b5f9198d","tid":2023723,"uid":200493,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"當時既學生都係爭取民主<br />\n我哋都係2014/2019先嚟醒<br />\n唔知我哋之後會唔會贏 你知道歷史都係贏既鳩up<br />\n例如64冇死人<br />\n到未來嘅人都會唔會覺得69/612/721/831/71/101...既係關自己事 覺得係同胞受打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567045eb108799b7cf44c6ee0aaf82378c97f406","tid":2023723,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:42:21.000Z","msg":"10年前身邊d同學覺得64要聲援同胞果陣我已經覺得64唔關我事"},{"pid":"2df46fa92057ba3ca28a2ab08f991e06a75aee55","tid":2023723,"uid":34424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:47:32.000Z","msg":"唔支持用「同胞」支那人還支那人 但我支持64集會呢啲要繼續搞 比班大中華膠集體打飛機 <br />\n因為今日64被打壓唔出聲 下次就到其他嘢被打壓"},{"pid":"d2320c734b065f6334af96732713d82be4c451cd","tid":2023723,"uid":279616,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"會悼念64當日死左既人，因為佢地為左自由民主既信念而犧牲，<br />\n<br />\n不過，死左既人無一個係我同胞，感覺同睇winter on fire, schindler&rsquo;s list一樣"},{"pid":"679d07a247f4d1ff9972bd23ccacc6f7873685b9","tid":2023723,"uid":50740,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:53:38.000Z","msg":"全靠64一代傳一代先可以延續民主精神，再引伸到今日遍地開花"},{